	<h1 class="title">Photoshop 25 周年，开始为适应一个新的世界而改变</h1>
	<div class="author-date clearfix">					
			<div class="author clearfix">
				<span class="name">Farhad Manjoo</span>
			</div>
		<span class="date smart-date" data-originDate="2015-02-22 19:01:27 +0800"></span>
	</div>
	<div class="banner">
			<img src="/system/articles/articleshows/6736/medium/6736.jpg?1436695965" alt="" />			
	</div>
	<!-- 传入参数：obj(aritcle, paper, card, mob) -->


